{"tid":444054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甘迺迪遇刺案3,000份密檔周四公開 特朗普「無意阻撓」","createTime":"2017-10-22T07:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T12:05:31.000Z","uid":20058,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"06c311aeed97c7997e93dc28a6ed774025f6fc0b","tid":444054,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普周六表示，會准許已故總統甘迺迪（John F Kennedy）遇刺案仍未曝光的機密檔案周四公開。<br />\n<br />\n甘迺迪1963年11月22日在達拉斯遇刺身亡。警方當日拘捕疑兇奧斯瓦爾德（ Lee Harvey Oswald），案發兩日後，他在警察總部遭槍殺。<br />\n<br />\n甘迺迪遇刺案大部份檔案已公開，但仍有逾3,000份一直保密。美國國會1992年授權所有有關甘迺迪遇刺案的機密文件，需要在25年內解封，除非總統認為公開機密會危害國防、情報、執法或外交關係，而公開密件的危害程度，甚於犧牲公眾知情權，否則一般情況下，所有到期資料都要公開。<br />\n<br />\n甘迺迪遇刺雖在半世紀前發生，但案件一直受歷史學家和陰謀論者關注。他們認為檔案保密時間已經太長，早應公開。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171022&amp;guid=57361902&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171022%26guid%3D57361902%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=D6Tn%2B3Jic7I3saX6PoHa2v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=56c246f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171022%26guid%3D57361902%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=2217a54a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171022&amp;guid=57361902&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4e9ceca00b3b79087f06391eff429af0cae12af0","tid":444054,"uid":21392,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應撚準備好出黎吠未"},{"pid":"05d50ff389d438d202c53ee176aa09e1310726a9","tid":444054,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e91e72c723a9ebac48d6af21536aae9a32e6102","tid":444054,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":